text: Magne Kleiven (27 July 1921 - 5 June 1999) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lillehammer
